{"id":277895,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/共识网-苏联第一家麦当劳开业，苏共惊恐万分/","date":"2013-02-05T05:30:36Z","modified":"2013-02-05T05:30:36Z","title":"共识网 | 苏联第一家麦当劳开业，苏共惊恐万分","content":"<div>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.21ccom.net/uploads/allimg/130205/44055_130205111623_1.jpg\" width=\"640\" border=\"0\" height=\"414\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p> 　　1990年1月31日,代表着西方资产阶级快餐文化的苏联第一家麦当劳餐厅在莫斯科盛大开业。人们为了能够品尝到这种在电视，电影以及报刊杂志上经常听说过的快餐而大排长龙。以至于排队就餐的队伍绵延数百米，盛况比上海世博那些热门场馆前的人流毫不相让。再强的壁垒封锁也无法阻挡人们对外来事物的好奇……当然对于麦当劳的进入苏共确实紧张万分，以至于排出宣传队到大街和校园里面宣讲“吃麦当劳，就是为美帝的霸权主义和侵略提供的枪炮”，但显然这些也无法抵御人们心中的好奇。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.21ccom.net/uploads/allimg/130205/44055_130205111710_1.jpg\" width=\"640\" border=\"0\" height=\"354\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.21ccom.net/uploads/allimg/130205/44055_130205111725_1.jpg\" width=\"640\" border=\"0\" height=\"359\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.21ccom.net/uploads/allimg/130205/44055_130205111740_1.jpg\" width=\"640\" border=\"0\" height=\"352\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.21ccom.net/uploads/allimg/130205/44055_130205111758_1.jpg\" width=\"640\" border=\"0\" height=\"381\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.21ccom.net/uploads/allimg/130205/44055_130205111813_1.jpg\" width=\"640\" border=\"0\" height=\"356\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.21ccom.net/uploads/allimg/130205/44055_130205111842_1.jpg\" width=\"640\" border=\"0\" height=\"377\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br